{"Id":489,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-muhammadmakin","Author":"Muhammad Makin","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://quranenc.com/check/chinese_makin/v1.0.0-csv.1 , https://quranenc.com/en/browse/chinese_makin , https://quranenc.com ,","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":105,"Text":"努哈的宗族曾否认使者。"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":106,"Text":"当时，他们的弟兄努哈对他们说：“你们怎么不敬畏安拉呢？"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":107,"Text":"我对于你们确是一个忠实的使者。"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":108,"Text":"故你们应当敬畏安拉，应当服从我。"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":109,"Text":"我不为传达使命而向你们索取任何报酬；我的报酬，只由众世界的主负担。"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":110,"Text":"故你们应当敬畏安拉，应当服从我。”"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":111,"Text":"他们说：“一些卑贱的人追随你，我们怎能信仰你呢？”"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":112,"Text":"他说：“我不知道他们做了什么事。"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":113,"Text":"我的主负责清算他们，假若你们知道。"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":114,"Text":"我绝不能驱逐信士，"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":115,"Text":"我只是一个直率的警告者。”"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":116,"Text":"他们说：“努哈啊！如果你不停止（宣传），你必遭石击。”"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":117,"Text":"他说：“我的主啊！我的宗族的确否认我。"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":118,"Text":"求你在我与他们之间进行裁判，求你拯救我和同我在一起的信士们。”"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":119,"Text":"我就拯救了他，以及在满载的船中与他共济的人。"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":120,"Text":"随后我溺杀了其余的人。"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":121,"Text":"此中确有一个迹象，但他们大半不信。"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":122,"Text":"你的主，确是万能的，确是至慈的。"}]}